WEBVTT

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:03.096
So what if I could make for you

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:04.600
a designer baby?

00:00:06.120 --> 00:00:08.416
What if you as a parent-to-be

00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:12.440
and I as a scientist decided
to go down that road together?

00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:15.296
What if we didn't?

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:18.096
What if we thought, "That's a bad idea,"

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:21.496
but many of our family,
friends and coworkers

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:23.160
did make that decision?

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:27.520
Let's fast-forward just 15 years from now.

00:00:27.960 --> 00:00:30.736
Let's pretend it's the year 2030,